WEBVTT

1
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:12.074
Watch Online Movies and Series for FREE
www.osdb.link/lm

2
00:00:19.720 --> 00:00:22.671
Tar is Arabic for “blood feud.”

3
00:00:22.957 --> 00:00:25.862
Restoration of wounded honor
or revenge for injustice caused.

4
00:00:26.538 --> 00:00:30.658
"May Allah protect us from the damned Satan. In
the name of Allah. the Beneficent. the Merciful.

5
00:00:31.858 --> 00:00:35.698
"...Ruler on the Day of Judgment.
We worship You and seek Your help.

6
00:00:36.218 --> 00:00:37.938
"Lead us to the straight path.

7
00:00:38.018 --> 00:00:40.154
"In the way of those whom
You have bestowed with mercy.

8
00:00:40.178 --> 00:00:43.578
“Not those on whom wrath has
fallen. nor those who are lost.”

9
00:00:43.658 --> 00:00:45.138
Amen.

10
00:00:51.658 --> 00:00:54.378
"Al-Fatiha" for the soul
Yusef Salem Muhammad al-Hayb.

11
00:00:54.458 --> 00:00:56.338
"We belong to Allah.
and to Him we will return."

12
00:01:00.858 --> 00:01:02.378
My dear Yusef.

13
00:01:04.338 --> 00:01:06.098
Inshallah. soon

14
00:01:06.658 --> 00:01:08.298
I will avenge your blood.

15
00:01:10.258 --> 00:01:11.938
Rest in peace.

16
00:02:39.618 --> 00:02:41.498
May Allah forgive you. Salem.

17
00:02:47.738 --> 00:02:49.194
What are you doing here?
are you crazy?

18
00:02:49.218 --> 00:02:50.778
Am I crazy?
You idiot.

19
00:02:52.538 --> 00:02:53.778
You almost blew my head off.

20
00:02:53.938 --> 00:02:55.754
You're breaking into my home what
do you think was going to happen. huh?

21
00:02:55.778 --> 00:02:57.418
I wasn't sure it was here.

22
00:02:57.498 --> 00:03:01.138
Your phone is turned off and your neighbors
are not exactly the right people to ask.

23
00:03:02.698 --> 00:03:03.738
The would-be tracker.

24
00:03:05.858 --> 00:03:09.378
It's beautiful here.
Quiet.
-Yes.

25
00:03:10.898 --> 00:03:12.378
How's your head?
Have you calmed down?

26
00:03:14.018 --> 00:03:15.898
A day like this. a day like that.

27
00:03:18.898 --> 00:03:21.138
I'm getting worse every day.

28
00:03:22.498 --> 00:03:24.578
You know daddy
loves all his children

29
00:03:24.658 --> 00:03:28.338
But Youssef was special.
-Yes.

30
00:03:28.418 --> 00:03:30.298
I have no one else to talk to at home

31
00:03:30.378 --> 00:03:33.178
And Noza doesn’t have the strength
to listen to my sadness anymore.

32
00:03:34.458 --> 00:03:35.898
So did you fall on me?

33
00:03:36.858 --> 00:03:40.618
Do you want to marry me?
Take him as a second wife?
Eh. Abu Musa?

34
00:03:46.258 --> 00:03:47.818
What's wrong with you?

35
00:03:47.898 --> 00:03:49.938
Do you pray to God every day?

36
00:03:52.058 --> 00:03:54.258
I'm waiting for Him to
come and take me away.

37
00:03:54.937 --> 00:03:58.698
I swear to you by the great Allah.
Abu Musa. I'm exhausted.

38
00:04:01.698 --> 00:04:02.818
I'm looking for answers.

39
00:04:07.377 --> 00:04:08.937
Honestly...

40
00:04:10.497 --> 00:04:12.698
I have something
what might interest you.

41
00:04:13.618 --> 00:04:15.618
There is progress in my investigation.

42
00:04:17.098 --> 00:04:19.818
Something has arrived.
-What is this?

43
00:04:21.578 --> 00:04:24.578
New video from your
house and Hagit's house.

44
00:04:25.257 --> 00:04:28.618
You can see Yusef and the
son of a bitch who did this.

45
00:04:28.898 --> 00:04:30.658
His name is Iyad Dahduh.

46
00:04:32.578 --> 00:04:37.218
This son of a bitch escaped from Gaza through
the crossing. Rafah during the second truce.

47
00:04:37.298 --> 00:04:38.538
He pretended to be wounded.

48
00:04:38.778 --> 00:04:40.497
Today he lives in Marseille.

49
00:04:41.858 --> 00:04:45.538
He has a business and a family.
As if nothing had happened.

50
00:04:46.937 --> 00:04:48.178
Where did you get this from?

51
00:04:49.258 --> 00:04:51.298
A friend sent it to me by mail.

52
00:04:51.818 --> 00:04:54.754
These. if you give them a million shekels.
they'll give you everything you want

53
00:04:54.778 --> 00:04:56.018
You didn't know?

54
00:04:56.377 --> 00:05:01.138
Believe me. all the crap that came
to me in the last two years was a lie.

55
00:05:01.258 --> 00:05:03.138
But this time it's true.

56
00:05:03.218 --> 00:05:04.818
Take it and see for yourself.

57
00:05:05.058 --> 00:05:07.698
My source tells me
that I got it from him.

58
00:05:11.418 --> 00:05:13.098
I want you to come with me to Marseille.

59
00:05:18.858 --> 00:05:20.618
Do you want me to go
with you to Marseille?

60
00:05:21.338 --> 00:05:23.218
Do you want me to go
with you to Marseille?

61
00:05:23.578 --> 00:05:24.938
And what are we going to do there?

62
00:05:25.098 --> 00:05:26.658
What do you want from me?

63
00:05:27.618 --> 00:05:29.218
What do you want from me?

64
00:05:29.377 --> 00:05:31.698
What do you want from me?
Abu Musa?

65
00:05:34.497 --> 00:05:36.658
Tell me
does this seem logical to you.

66
00:05:36.818 --> 00:05:40.258
That this son of a bitch lives there in
Marseilles. as if nothing had happened?

67
00:05:40.778 --> 00:05:42.298
I'm no longer there.

68
00:05:42.978 --> 00:05:44.978
I'm not there anymore. Salem.

69
00:05:45.458 --> 00:05:46.818
Eli.

70
00:05:47.738 --> 00:05:49.778
Клянусь Аллахом. это кровная месть.

71
00:05:50.138 --> 00:05:52.938
Who. if not you. knows
what blood feud means?

72
00:05:53.738 --> 00:05:56.858
If we don't do this. this day will
haunt us for the rest of our lives.

73
00:05:57.658 --> 00:06:00.298
This is blood feud. You must
avenge your family's blood.

74
00:07:07.818 --> 00:07:11.378
Very good.
Don't lose sight.

75
00:07:13.978 --> 00:07:16.778
Okay. now try to focus on the
memory that came up. okay?

76
00:07:16.858 --> 00:07:18.098
Describe it to me.

77
00:07:50.058 --> 00:07:55.138
I'm outside. behind the iron

78
00:07:56.938 --> 00:07:58.458
And I look inside.

79
00:07:59.338 --> 00:08:00.978
What do you see inside?

80
00:08:05.618 --> 00:08:06.898
There's someone there.

81
00:08:10.858 --> 00:08:12.218
They're dead.

82
00:08:15.657 --> 00:08:18.498
Everyone is dead.
-Describe them to me.

83
00:08:22.498 --> 00:08:23.978
They are children.

84
00:08:26.657 --> 00:08:27.938
Beautiful.

85
00:08:32.938 --> 00:08:34.777
At the age of my children.

86
00:08:45.298 --> 00:08:46.818
And full of blood.

87
00:08:51.418 --> 00:08:52.858
And then there was an explosion.

88
00:08:55.338 --> 00:08:57.258
Doron. where are you?

89
00:08:58.538 --> 00:09:00.538
Stay with me. Doron.
What do you see?

90
00:09:05.338 --> 00:09:07.938
Full of smoke and smell.

91
00:09:09.138 --> 00:09:10.218
Smell?

92
00:09:11.738 --> 00:09:12.938
What?

93
00:09:15.098 --> 00:09:16.378
Meat.

94
00:09:25.858 --> 00:09:27.058
Yes.

95
00:09:35.978 --> 00:09:37.098
I can't.

96
00:09:37.418 --> 00:09:39.298
I don't understand
why can't I remember.

97
00:09:40.618 --> 00:09:42.058
I'm trying to connect all the dots

98
00:09:42.138 --> 00:09:44.178
And I don't understand
How can I not connect this.

99
00:09:44.258 --> 00:09:48.178
You're making good progress. We're
approaching slowly. that's normal.

100
00:09:48.258 --> 00:09:50.658
I understand that you want to
connect everything. but slowly.

101
00:09:50.738 --> 00:09:52.234
How did eight hours
disappear from my life?

102
00:09:52.258 --> 00:09:53.554
Eight hours of my life disappeared.

103
00:09:53.578 --> 00:09:56.418
Doron. you are inside the process.
and we are on the right track.

104
00:09:56.897 --> 00:09:58.618
Don't judge yourself.

105
00:10:00.538 --> 00:10:02.298
I don't know if I
managed to save her.

106
00:10:04.698 --> 00:10:06.058
It's driving me crazy.

107
00:10:23.498 --> 00:10:27.458
I bought you something. There. behind.
-To me? -Yes.

108
00:10:27.738 --> 00:10:29.258
In that white bag there.

109
00:10:36.858 --> 00:10:39.098
What is it. today is my
birthday. I didn’t know?

110
00:10:42.338 --> 00:10:43.338
Beautiful?

111
00:10:44.578 --> 00:10:45.578
Yes.

112
00:10:45.777 --> 00:10:47.378
With buttons. blue?

113
00:10:48.378 --> 00:10:50.338
You wear these dark shirts all the time.

114
00:10:51.978 --> 00:10:54.378
You have such beautiful
eyes so let everyone see them.

115
00:10:57.657 --> 00:10:58.818
Thank you.

116
00:11:09.578 --> 00:11:12.258
Who is it here. Eli?
What is he doing here?

117
00:11:12.338 --> 00:11:14.098
What. were you talking?
-No.

118
00:11:21.818 --> 00:11:25.098
Look who's here.
Messiah on a pickup truck.

119
00:11:25.698 --> 00:11:27.338
The donkey wouldn't start.

120
00:11:28.698 --> 00:11:31.738
I missed you.
-Me too.
-Very.

121
00:11:35.258 --> 00:11:38.018
What? Can I hug or are
you maintaining privacy?

122
00:11:38.098 --> 00:11:40.098
Gali. you are family. that's normal.

123
00:11:41.538 --> 00:11:44.178
Fine.
Enough.
Come on. please.

124
00:11:47.858 --> 00:11:49.777
Don't move your head
only with your eyes.

125
00:11:50.938 --> 00:11:53.538
Understood? The more
I speed up the pace

126
00:11:53.698 --> 00:11:56.738
Slowly the memories come.

127
00:12:00.897 --> 00:12:02.897
But the truth is it works
this thing. brother.

128
00:12:03.058 --> 00:12:05.338
It's like I'm concentrating
the picture pops up

129
00:12:05.418 --> 00:12:09.618
And then I put together a timeline for that day.
-Really.

130
00:12:12.298 --> 00:12:14.738
Wow.
Cool. brother.
-What's going on. Eli?

131
00:12:17.618 --> 00:12:20.458
Salem came to see me today.
-Wow.

132
00:12:21.618 --> 00:12:25.258
How is he? Last time when
I saw him. he was broken.

133
00:12:26.578 --> 00:12:30.738
Yes. come on. brother. You don't
know what it's like to lose a child.

134
00:12:31.298 --> 00:12:33.258
And so that you don’t know. God forbid.

135
00:12:34.578 --> 00:12:37.218
He is still looking for those
fighters of Nukhba. who killed Yusef?

136
00:12:38.698 --> 00:12:41.898
Searching with all his might.
-Really.

137
00:12:42.858 --> 00:12:44.098
And what will he do?

138
00:12:45.338 --> 00:12:47.778
Don't know.
-What. blood feud?

139
00:12:48.658 --> 00:12:51.938
Eli. don't let him put
ideas into your head. okay?

140
00:12:53.458 --> 00:12:56.538
Screw him with his
Bedouin nonsense.

141
00:12:56.618 --> 00:13:00.418
Brother. what you and Salem went through...
this is the hardest thing in the world

142
00:13:00.818 --> 00:13:04.058
But nothing. nothing will bring
Hagit and the children back to you.

143
00:13:23.098 --> 00:13:26.338
I promise you we won't harm you.

144
00:13:26.698 --> 00:13:28.258
We follow the path of Allah.

145
00:13:34.538 --> 00:13:35.818
What is he doing?

146
00:13:36.538 --> 00:13:37.658
There's no one here.

147
00:13:37.738 --> 00:13:39.418
You son of a bitch.

148
00:15:32.858 --> 00:15:35.018
Hey. you're awake.

149
00:15:39.098 --> 00:15:40.498
They are clean.

150
00:15:42.978 --> 00:15:44.258
Yes.

151
00:15:47.538 --> 00:15:48.978
Everything is fine?

152
00:15:50.418 --> 00:15:53.778
This is Eli.
He worries me.
-Why?

153
00:15:55.258 --> 00:16:00.018
When he was here. he talked to
me about Salem. about his son.

154
00:16:01.418 --> 00:16:03.578
I'll go check in the morning
what's happening to him.

155
00:16:05.498 --> 00:16:08.338
But you're in therapy.
-Yes.

156
00:16:09.098 --> 00:16:11.218
I'll talk to Dr. Peled.
everything is fine.

157
00:16:12.018 --> 00:16:13.618
Doron. it's not your fault.

158
00:16:15.458 --> 00:16:17.378
You don't have to take
responsibility for him.

159
00:16:19.258 --> 00:16:20.618
I know.

160
00:16:22.098 --> 00:16:25.978
But he is alone.
Gali is not with him.

161
00:16:39.698 --> 00:16:41.178
Next one please.

162
00:16:46.138 --> 00:16:47.738
What is the purpose of your trip?

163
00:16:48.178 --> 00:16:49.538
I'm visiting a friend.

164
00:16:49.618 --> 00:16:50.898
Where does he live?

165
00:17:03.858 --> 00:17:05.658
Take off your hat.

166
00:17:10.978 --> 00:17:13.378
Go through the security check
please.

167
00:17:14.338 --> 00:17:15.898
Have a problem?

168
00:17:15.978 --> 00:17:18.138
Sir. please go to security.

169
00:17:20.858 --> 00:17:22.058
Next one please.

170
00:17:51.018 --> 00:17:52.898
Be careful with her.

171
00:17:55.178 --> 00:17:56.898
Take off your shoes.

172
00:18:01.418 --> 00:18:03.258
Next one please.

173
00:18:35.098 --> 00:18:37.098
Tell me. was the inspection
involving penetration?

174
00:18:38.538 --> 00:18:40.058
Come on. go. go.

175
00:18:40.258 --> 00:18:42.457
You know that every time
when I return to Israel.

176
00:18:42.538 --> 00:18:44.178
Am I being tested?

177
00:18:45.298 --> 00:18:47.738
Very good.
This is how it should be with you Arabs.

178
00:18:48.658 --> 00:18:50.178
Come on. go. go.

179
00:18:52.498 --> 00:18:54.138
Your mother.

180
00:18:58.298 --> 00:19:01.538
I just visited Eli.
-Well?
Have you calmed down?
-Not really.

181
00:19:01.618 --> 00:19:03.498
He's not at home.
He doesn't answer phones.

182
00:19:04.378 --> 00:19:05.634
I asked the children
in the settlement there.

183
00:19:05.658 --> 00:19:07.938
They told me he left last night.
-OK.

184
00:19:08.018 --> 00:19:11.457
So where are you?
-I'm on my way to Rakhat. to Salem.

185
00:19:11.697 --> 00:19:14.378
Maybe these two crazy people are sitting there together.
-Fine.

186
00:19:14.778 --> 00:19:18.178
Okay. I'll talk to you later. okay?
-Bye. -Bye. honey. bye.

187
00:19:50.058 --> 00:19:52.018
Musa.
Salaam Alaikum.

188
00:19:52.098 --> 00:19:54.697
I served with your father.
Can I come in?

189
00:20:00.738 --> 00:20:02.658
Salaam alaikum
-Vaaleikum assalam.

190
00:20:02.738 --> 00:20:05.098
I'm Doron Cabilio.
-I know who you are.

191
00:20:05.697 --> 00:20:07.298
I've seen you before.

192
00:20:08.378 --> 00:20:10.018
Can I exchange a few words with you?

193
00:20:10.898 --> 00:20:12.338
Please.

194
00:20:13.457 --> 00:20:17.738
Since Yusef's death.
Satan controls his thoughts.

195
00:20:17.818 --> 00:20:20.338
He can't stop thinking
about the idea of ​​revenge.

196
00:20:21.178 --> 00:20:22.697
When was the last time you saw him?

197
00:20:22.978 --> 00:20:25.338
Last night.
I saw him packing his suitcase

198
00:20:25.418 --> 00:20:27.298
When I got up in the
morning. I didn't find him

199
00:20:27.778 --> 00:20:29.178
How was he?

200
00:20:29.578 --> 00:20:31.178
How has he been these last few days?

201
00:20:38.658 --> 00:20:41.738
Listen.
I want to show you something.

202
00:20:42.898 --> 00:20:47.258
Only he has the key.
He did not allow anyone to enter.

203
00:21:10.217 --> 00:21:12.338
For long hours he
locked himself here.

204
00:21:22.418 --> 00:21:24.298
He offered a reward
of one million shekels

205
00:21:24.378 --> 00:21:27.018
To the one who comes out to the
people of Nukhba. who killed Yusef.

206
00:21:35.018 --> 00:21:36.578
Has he received many calls?

207
00:21:36.658 --> 00:21:37.697
Dozens.

208
00:21:37.778 --> 00:21:39.338
Hundreds. maybe.

209
00:21:40.018 --> 00:21:43.898
He checked every detail. every number.
I was doing just that all the time.

210
00:21:48.538 --> 00:21:49.538
Is this his?

211
00:21:50.298 --> 00:21:51.338
Yes.

212
00:21:57.178 --> 00:21:59.457
I don't know the password.

213
00:21:59.578 --> 00:22:01.858
Can I take it?
-Where?

214
00:22:02.298 --> 00:22:05.457
To my friend.
He understands computers.

215
00:22:06.217 --> 00:22:07.578
Fine.

216
00:22:34.338 --> 00:22:36.538
Salaam Aleikum
-Vaaleikum Assalam.

217
00:22:36.618 --> 00:22:38.697
Tell me. is Rami at home?
-Who's asking?

218
00:22:38.778 --> 00:22:40.178
Tell him. Al-Badawi ("Bedouin").

219
00:22:43.058 --> 00:22:44.338
Just a minute.

220
00:22:52.217 --> 00:22:53.338
Come in.

221
00:23:00.818 --> 00:23:02.258
Salaam Aleikum

222
00:23:06.618 --> 00:23:07.978
Where is the money?

223
00:23:08.778 --> 00:23:10.457
Here they are.

224
00:23:10.578 --> 00:23:11.858
Please.

225
00:23:16.578 --> 00:23:18.058
Now it's your turn.

226
00:23:24.498 --> 00:23:25.978
This restaurant is his.

227
00:23:28.217 --> 00:23:30.178
Go see him at the end of the evening.

228
00:23:30.258 --> 00:23:31.498
He won't have many people

229
00:23:31.578 --> 00:23:33.697
But very “serious”
people come there.

230
00:23:34.778 --> 00:23:36.457
How did you find him?

231
00:23:37.178 --> 00:23:39.978
Since the beginning of the war.
many from Gaza have come here.

232
00:23:40.058 --> 00:23:44.498
Everyone is quiet. except Dahduh.
he doesn't close his mouth.

233
00:23:45.258 --> 00:23:47.378
One day he showed me a video

234
00:23:47.457 --> 00:23:50.697
I told him: “Why did you kill
this poor child? He is an Arab."

235
00:23:51.178 --> 00:23:52.938
Do you know what he answered me?

236
00:23:53.258 --> 00:23:57.058
He told me: “This damned -
Jewish dog."

237
00:24:06.938 --> 00:24:08.298
Anything else?

238
00:24:09.258 --> 00:24:11.098
What about what I asked you?

239
00:24:11.217 --> 00:24:14.178
I told you I need an additional
payment. another 20 thousand.

240
00:24:20.138 --> 00:24:21.898
It's all here.

241
00:24:57.658 --> 00:25:01.458
Our product will reveal your
real financial performance online.

242
00:25:01.538 --> 00:25:04.898
The most important thing is that
this service is completely confidential.

243
00:25:04.978 --> 00:25:06.658
Of course you understand this.

244
00:25:06.978 --> 00:25:08.698
In order to...

245
00:25:15.258 --> 00:25:17.818
It took my people three
minutes. to hack a computer.

246
00:25:17.898 --> 00:25:19.498
It's good that you came to me with this.

247
00:25:19.818 --> 00:25:21.498
We follow the path of Allah.

248
00:25:21.578 --> 00:25:23.218
It's enough. I promise you.

249
00:25:23.298 --> 00:25:24.858
We follow the path of Allah.

250
00:25:24.938 --> 00:25:26.698
This is Eli's house on the kibbutz.

251
00:25:26.978 --> 00:25:28.058
Open the door!

252
00:25:28.138 --> 00:25:31.898
Inside the shelter is Yusef. who
lived next to them. the son of Salem.

253
00:25:33.498 --> 00:25:35.314
In the name of Allah. the
Beneficent. the Merciful.

254
00:25:35.338 --> 00:25:37.218
You son of a bitch.

255
00:25:42.858 --> 00:25:45.978
I used my remaining connections in
the service to run facial recognition.

256
00:25:46.538 --> 00:25:48.698
The one in this video
is This is Iyad Dahduh.

257
00:25:48.858 --> 00:25:50.858
Action movie Nukhba.
who now lives in Marseille.

258
00:25:52.418 --> 00:25:55.738
How's Marseille?
-Marseille. he is Marcel.

259
00:25:56.258 --> 00:25:59.058
And guess who got on
flight 322 there this morning.

260
00:26:00.018 --> 00:26:02.858
Okay. so what do we do?
-Good question.

261
00:26:04.658 --> 00:26:06.378
Yes. Gabi?
What did you want?

262
00:26:10.578 --> 00:26:12.018
What's happened?
Did someone die?

263
00:26:12.378 --> 00:26:16.978
Meet Leah. Leah. this is
Doron. an old service comrade.

264
00:26:17.058 --> 00:26:18.378
I've heard several stories.

265
00:26:18.458 --> 00:26:20.978
Nice to finally meet you.
-Me too. very pleased.

266
00:26:22.218 --> 00:26:25.138
What is this? What are you looking at there?
- It's none of your business.

267
00:26:25.698 --> 00:26:28.034
Tell me. how are things going with
the supply of connectors for the system?

268
00:26:28.058 --> 00:26:29.594
We have a meeting tomorrow.
I need to come with answers.

269
00:26:29.618 --> 00:26:33.058
We work 24/7 on the lines.
Everything will be ready on time.

270
00:26:33.298 --> 00:26:35.418
Do you know why her name is Leah?
-No.

271
00:26:35.498 --> 00:26:37.418
Because “you got it”. “I got it too”.

272
00:26:37.858 --> 00:26:39.698
Go. go to your job.

273
00:26:40.618 --> 00:26:42.298
Come on. well. accelerate. accelerate.

274
00:26:50.138 --> 00:26:51.578
Who is this lady?

275
00:26:51.658 --> 00:26:54.098
My fixer.
Super gun. brilliant.

276
00:26:54.178 --> 00:26:56.538
I pulled her out of service.
A bright future awaits her.

277
00:26:56.618 --> 00:26:59.778
Tell me. is your passport valid?

278
00:27:01.098 --> 00:27:04.058
For what?
-I want to take you on a cruise to the Maldives. why else?

279
00:27:04.138 --> 00:27:05.874
Someone needs to stop
these two crazy people.

280
00:27:05.898 --> 00:27:07.138
I'm off topic. Gabi.

281
00:27:07.218 --> 00:27:09.194
What does “off topic” mean?
Then who's in the know?

282
00:27:09.218 --> 00:27:11.234
Sagi and Nurit are about
to give birth in Australia.

283
00:27:11.258 --> 00:27:13.114
Steve works as a body
armorer for oligarchs in London.

284
00:27:13.138 --> 00:27:16.418
Gabi. you're just hysterical.
-Doron. you must fly now.

285
00:27:16.498 --> 00:27:19.298
Before your friend goes and
does something that will ruin his life.

286
00:27:33.258 --> 00:27:34.538
Hello.

287
00:27:42.538 --> 00:27:44.338
I thought we were already over this.

288
00:27:47.538 --> 00:27:49.138
Eli needs me.

289
00:27:50.418 --> 00:27:52.418
Doron. there's always something.

290
00:27:53.458 --> 00:27:54.898
What about what you need?

291
00:28:01.698 --> 00:28:03.698
Don't you remember what state you were in?

292
00:28:04.778 --> 00:28:07.178
After you all
almost died in Jenin

293
00:28:07.578 --> 00:28:08.858
And then October.

294
00:28:12.818 --> 00:28:13.938
I remember.

295
00:28:44.858 --> 00:28:46.538
Shall we pray?
-Let's.

296
00:28:48.098 --> 00:28:50.538
"Lead us to the straight path.

297
00:28:50.618 --> 00:28:52.274
"In the way of those whom
You have bestowed with mercy.

298
00:28:52.298 --> 00:28:54.738
“Not those on whom wrath has
fallen. nor those who are lost.”

299
00:28:54.818 --> 00:28:56.458
"To the great. heroic and formidable God.

300
00:28:56.538 --> 00:28:59.298
"To God Most High. who does good
deeds and possesses everything.

301
00:28:59.378 --> 00:29:00.434
"And remembering the
mercies of the fathers.

302
00:29:00.458 --> 00:29:02.982
"The King who kills and gives life.
and cultivating salvation

303
00:29:03.006 --> 00:29:05.098
"And You are faithful
to give life to the dead."

304
00:29:05.178 --> 00:29:07.018
"Blessed are You. Lord..."

305
00:29:29.338 --> 00:29:30.498
This is him.

306
00:29:34.898 --> 00:29:37.378
Look at this son of a
bitch how he enjoys life.

307
00:29:43.058 --> 00:29:45.778
Salem. that's enough.

308
00:29:46.178 --> 00:29:49.058
We'll pass on his information to
the police. intelligence. and that's it.

309
00:29:50.418 --> 00:29:53.458
It's that son of a bitch who broke
into your house and burned it down.

310
00:30:10.298 --> 00:30:12.578
First of all. let's talk to him.
Let's make sure it's him.

311
00:30:15.058 --> 00:30:16.378
You understand?

312
00:30:19.178 --> 00:30:21.498
Salem. do you understand?

313
00:30:32.298 --> 00:30:34.338
Thank you.
-My soul. this is an honor for us.

314
00:30:34.418 --> 00:30:37.138
Say hello to Syria.
To your health.
-Thank you.

315
00:30:43.098 --> 00:30:45.178
Salaam Aleikum
-Vaaleikum Assalam.

316
00:30:45.418 --> 00:30:47.274
What. are you closing already?
Already put out the fire?

317
00:30:47.298 --> 00:30:50.098
I swear by Allah. my brothers. as
you can see. I am already closing.

318
00:30:50.178 --> 00:30:51.858
We beg you brother

319
00:30:51.938 --> 00:30:54.618
We are your brothers and we are hungry.
We are after a long trip.

320
00:30:54.698 --> 00:30:56.218
We arrived straight from the airport.

321
00:30:56.298 --> 00:30:59.298
They didn't even give
us peanuts on the plane.

322
00:31:05.978 --> 00:31:07.058
Please come in.

323
00:31:07.938 --> 00:31:09.178
Thank you.

324
00:31:11.058 --> 00:31:13.258
It's good that the coals are still burning.

325
00:31:16.858 --> 00:31:18.658
Where are you guys from?

326
00:31:18.818 --> 00:31:20.498
From Jordan. from Amman.

327
00:31:20.578 --> 00:31:21.858
Come on. from Jordan?

328
00:31:21.938 --> 00:31:23.858
Do you know anyone there?
-Well. of course.

329
00:31:23.938 --> 00:31:25.858
I have a big family there
in Vihdat.

330
00:31:25.938 --> 00:31:27.378
Palestinians.

331
00:31:27.498 --> 00:31:28.818
We are from Aqaba.

332
00:31:28.898 --> 00:31:30.378
Very nice.
-Me too.

333
00:31:30.458 --> 00:31:31.858
At your service. Salah

334
00:31:31.938 --> 00:31:34.618
And this quiet and shy
man's name is Ahmad.

335
00:31:35.338 --> 00:31:36.418
Very nice.
-Greetings.

336
00:31:36.498 --> 00:31:39.178
At your service. Iyad. Very nice.
-Greetings.

337
00:31:39.418 --> 00:31:42.538
Then sit down and I'll
cook you a great dinner.

338
00:31:44.138 --> 00:31:48.698
Don’t bother. prepare us something
from what you have. something light.

339
00:31:48.778 --> 00:31:52.738
A believer in Allah and the Day of
Judgment must respect his guests.

340
00:31:56.418 --> 00:31:59.418
Your accent makes you sound
like you're from Gaza or the Negev.

341
00:32:00.138 --> 00:32:02.098
Yes. I'm from Gaza. brother.

342
00:32:05.418 --> 00:32:07.218
Were you there during the war?

343
00:32:07.298 --> 00:32:10.698
If I had been there during the
war. We wouldn't stand and talk here.

344
00:32:10.778 --> 00:32:13.458
My family and I came
here a few years ago.

345
00:32:14.138 --> 00:32:16.418
The Jews gave us the Nakba.

346
00:32:16.578 --> 00:32:18.858
May Allah take revenge on them.

347
00:32:18.978 --> 00:32:20.938
Many of my comrades fell as martyrs.

348
00:32:21.298 --> 00:32:23.538
Allah is our helper and savior.

349
00:32:25.338 --> 00:32:27.978
Did you also have a restaurant in Gaza?

350
00:32:28.098 --> 00:32:30.378
I had a different life in Gaza.

351
00:32:30.458 --> 00:32:32.698
I had a small carpentry workshop.
and I felt good.

352
00:32:33.178 --> 00:32:36.898
When we arrived in Europe. I saw that people
here want everything quickly and simply.

353
00:32:36.978 --> 00:32:38.538
I made them fast food.

354
00:32:38.618 --> 00:32:39.818
That is. Ikea.

355
00:32:54.938 --> 00:32:55.978
Salaam Aleikum

356
00:32:56.058 --> 00:32:58.298
Abu Muhammad?
-Yes.

357
00:32:58.578 --> 00:33:00.658
They're looking for you. boy. be careful.

358
00:33:14.498 --> 00:33:16.418
Yes. my brothers.
I have no meat left here.

359
00:33:16.498 --> 00:33:19.018
I'll go downstairs and get it
from the refrigerator downstairs.

360
00:33:19.258 --> 00:33:20.538
Fine.

361
00:33:32.298 --> 00:33:33.658
Muhammad. my son.

362
00:33:35.498 --> 00:33:37.738
Run to Uncle Naji
tell him to come here quickly.

363
00:33:37.818 --> 00:33:39.074
Tell him to take his weapon with him.

364
00:33:39.098 --> 00:33:42.178
Why. dad? What's happened?
-Shhh... Speak quietly.

365
00:33:43.218 --> 00:33:45.138
Go. go. go.

366
00:33:45.218 --> 00:33:48.058
Tell him to come in through the back door.

367
00:34:25.418 --> 00:34:27.018
Drop the knife.

368
00:34:27.098 --> 00:34:28.337
Give it up.

369
00:34:29.738 --> 00:34:31.018
Back.

370
00:34:31.858 --> 00:34:33.098
Back!

371
00:34:41.618 --> 00:34:42.738
Is everything okay upstairs?

372
00:34:42.898 --> 00:34:44.098
I locked the door.

373
00:34:44.378 --> 00:34:45.778
There is not a single dog upstairs.

374
00:34:46.138 --> 00:34:48.618
Tried to get a knife. son of a bitch.

375
00:34:49.498 --> 00:34:51.817
You. dog.
-No. no. please.

376
00:35:07.658 --> 00:35:08.938
Please people.

377
00:35:25.618 --> 00:35:27.698
Gabi.
-Welcome.

378
00:35:28.618 --> 00:35:29.618
Talk to me.

379
00:35:29.778 --> 00:35:31.793
I'm sending you the address
of the target restaurant.

380
00:35:31.817 --> 00:35:32.978
Go there.

381
00:35:36.658 --> 00:35:39.418
Doron. are you with me?
-What?
Yes. yes. yes. I'm listening.

382
00:35:39.498 --> 00:35:41.018
Repeat what you said.

383
00:35:41.178 --> 00:35:43.378
I'm sending you the address.
Go there now.

384
00:35:43.698 --> 00:35:45.698
I really hope
that it's not too late.

385
00:35:46.098 --> 00:35:50.297
Tell the driver to take the A 55.
-Okay. I understand.
Thank you.

386
00:35:58.498 --> 00:35:59.858
Wake up.

387
00:36:00.258 --> 00:36:01.538
Wake up!

388
00:36:12.538 --> 00:36:14.018
Who are you. Israelis?

389
00:36:14.378 --> 00:36:15.498
Are you Jewish?

390
00:36:15.578 --> 00:36:17.218
He's Jewish

391
00:36:17.538 --> 00:36:18.978
And I...

392
00:36:19.058 --> 00:36:20.418
Muslim.

393
00:36:20.858 --> 00:36:24.538
Like my son. whom you killed while he
was praying and reading Al-Fatiha. you dog.

394
00:36:24.618 --> 00:36:26.458
I swear to Allah. I have
nothing to do with it.

395
00:36:28.858 --> 00:36:29.778
Enough is enough. I promise you...

396
00:36:29.858 --> 00:36:30.658
Look carefully.

397
00:36:30.738 --> 00:36:31.538
We won't harm you.

398
00:36:31.618 --> 00:36:32.498
Look here.

399
00:36:32.578 --> 00:36:34.138
We follow the path of Allah.

400
00:36:35.458 --> 00:36:36.498
Do you see?

401
00:36:36.578 --> 00:36:38.418
You son of a bitch.

402
00:36:40.578 --> 00:36:42.778
Your turn will come soon.

403
00:36:43.778 --> 00:36:46.058
It's good that you filmed everything.

404
00:36:46.578 --> 00:36:49.138
Otherwise we would have come
here and just wasted our time.

405
00:36:49.938 --> 00:36:51.378
What do you say. Iyad?

406
00:36:53.418 --> 00:36:55.138
Are you praying?
You. Satan.

407
00:36:55.218 --> 00:36:57.418
You will soon burn in hellfire.

408
00:36:57.498 --> 00:36:59.337
Wait a second. Salem.

409
00:37:07.698 --> 00:37:09.337
Look at them.

410
00:37:10.738 --> 00:37:12.297
Look.

411
00:37:15.138 --> 00:37:16.698
Did you kill them?

412
00:37:19.938 --> 00:37:21.258
No. not me.

413
00:37:28.218 --> 00:37:29.978
Do you know who killed them?

414
00:37:32.018 --> 00:37:33.337
No.

415
00:37:42.098 --> 00:37:43.618
My commander did this.

416
00:37:45.258 --> 00:37:46.778
I can help you.

417
00:37:48.498 --> 00:37:50.554
And your son... I have nothing
to do with what happened to him.

418
00:37:50.578 --> 00:37:52.938
You know
You can't disobey orders.

419
00:37:53.018 --> 00:37:54.698
What is the commander's name?

420
00:37:55.538 --> 00:37:56.738
Maher Zeitoun.

421
00:37:56.817 --> 00:37:59.218
He lives here.
Here. here in Marseille.

422
00:37:59.297 --> 00:38:01.034
I didn't know about it what
was supposed to happen there.

423
00:38:01.058 --> 00:38:03.418
All I knew was that we were
just going to steal and destroy.

424
00:38:03.778 --> 00:38:04.978
Liar!

425
00:38:05.058 --> 00:38:06.658
Are you lying?
You. dog.

426
00:38:06.738 --> 00:38:08.218
What's his address?

427
00:38:15.658 --> 00:38:17.138
He works in the center.

428
00:38:17.218 --> 00:38:18.938
Which center?
-Yuma Center.

429
00:38:19.578 --> 00:38:21.458
Center for refugees and migrants.

430
00:38:21.698 --> 00:38:23.194
There are several young
men from Gaza with him.

431
00:38:23.218 --> 00:38:25.018
Hamas?
-I have nothing to do with it at all.

432
00:38:25.098 --> 00:38:26.938
You see. I have a restaurant.

433
00:38:28.578 --> 00:38:30.098
I'm just a little soldier.

434
00:38:30.178 --> 00:38:31.698
I beg you.

435
00:38:32.418 --> 00:38:33.658
I beg you.

436
00:38:33.817 --> 00:38:36.018
I have children
I have small children.

437
00:38:36.098 --> 00:38:37.178
I beg you.

438
00:39:01.138 --> 00:39:02.337
You dog!

439
00:39:03.218 --> 00:39:04.498
Salem!

440
00:39:21.658 --> 00:39:23.618
Salem. Salem.

441
00:39:24.658 --> 00:39:26.858
Be with me.
Stay with me. Salem.

442
00:39:28.498 --> 00:39:31.978
Be with me. Be with
me. You'll be fine. okay?

443
00:39:32.058 --> 00:39:33.658
Run after him.

444
00:39:34.258 --> 00:39:35.458
Don't let him escape.

445
00:39:35.538 --> 00:39:38.618
Put your hand here. Click here. okay?
-Fine.

446
00:40:27.018 --> 00:40:28.218
Thank you very much.

447
00:42:13.738 --> 00:42:14.858
Crap.

448
00:42:17.297 --> 00:42:18.898
What are you doing here. brother?

449
00:42:21.098 --> 00:42:23.898
What is this?
What happened here?

